task.summary: Added creatures to the game with interactions
ItemHandler now prints item info instead of returning the string
The enemy attack text during fights are now random
Removed MapEntityMapper, and made it possible to have multiple characters of the same type in the cave
Check for duplicates in backpack before picking up item
Now supports multiple caves and loads cave name from same file as the map
Moved the game loop to game state
Added test for the item handler
Moved item handling dialog to own class to make it more testable
Added colors to the ui output
